						<p><hi rend="italic">Broken slab lying in Survey No. 2.</hi></p>						

						<p>15th Century A.D.</p>						

						<p>This record, in characters of about the <hi rend="bold">15th Century A.D.,</hi> is dated the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Raudra [Pausha, śu.] 5, Tuesday.</hi> The details cannot be verified. It records the death of Mallayya, son of Bhayiraya-nāyaka, and younger brother Māchaya. </p>						

